# AluVerse - Clean Project Structure

## Root Files
├── .gitattributes              # Git file handling
├── .gitignore                  # Git ignore rules  
├── DEPLOYMENT.md               # Deployment guide
├── README.md                   # Project documentation
├── package.json                # Dependencies & scripts
├── package-lock.json           # Locked dependency versions

## Configuration Files  
├── eslint.config.js            # ESLint linting rules
├── postcss.config.js           # PostCSS configuration
├── tailwind.config.js          # Tailwind CSS configuration
├── tsconfig.json               # TypeScript configuration
├── vite.config.ts              # Vite build tool configuration
├── index.html                  # Main HTML template

## Deployment Configurations
├── vercel.json                 # Vercel deployment (recommended)
├── netlify.toml                # Netlify deployment

## Directories
├── public/                     # Static assets
│   ├── .htaccess              # Apache server config
│   ├── _redirects             # Netlify redirects
│   └── demo-dataset.json      # Demo data
│
├── src/                       # Source code
│   ├── components/            # React components
│   ├── contexts/              # React contexts
│   ├── types/                 # TypeScript definitions
│   ├── utils/                 # Utility functions
│   ├── App.tsx                # Main app component
│   ├── main.tsx               # Entry point
│   ├── index.css              # Global styles
│   └── vite-env.d.ts          # Vite environment types
│
└── dist/                      # Production build (generated)
    ├── assets/                # Bundled assets
    ├── index.html             # Built HTML
    └── demo-dataset.json      # Demo data copy

## Removed Items
✗ .github/                    # GitHub templates & workflows
✗ firebase.json               # Firebase config (redundant)
✗ CHANGELOG.md                # Change log (unnecessary)
